<section class="space-y-6">
  <div class="rounded-2xl border border-amber-200 bg-amber-50/80 p-6 dark:border-amber-700 dark:bg-amber-900/20">
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-amber-900 dark:text-amber-200">Hidden extras & console commands</h2>
    <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-amber-900/80 dark:text-amber-100/80">
      Hidden links or achievements stay invisible until a visitor opens the browser console and runs our helper functions. Use this tab to preview what ships.
    </p>
    <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm text-amber-900 dark:text-amber-100">
      <li><code class="rounded bg-white/60 px-2 py-1 text-xs text-slate-900">techub.revealHidden()</code> — toggles hidden items on/off for the current profile.</li>
      <li><code class="rounded bg-white/60 px-2 py-1 text-xs text-slate-900">techub.hiddenCount()</code> — prints how many secrets are available.</li>
      <li><code class="rounded bg-white/60 px-2 py-1 text-xs text-slate-900">techub.iddqd()</code> — enables the Doom-inspired glow (and logs an analytics event).</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-amber-900/70 dark:text-amber-100/70">Hidden items still collect analytics and respect your style choices. Add an optional secret code to any link to create scavenger-hunt style unlocks.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white/80 p-6 shadow-sm dark:border-slate-700 dark:bg-slate-900/70">
    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100">Hidden item summary</h3>
    <% hidden_links = links.select(&:hidden?).count %>
    <% hidden_achievements = achievements.select(&:hidden?).count %>
    <% hidden_experiences = experiences.select(&:hidden?).count %>
    <% total = hidden_links + hidden_achievements + hidden_experiences %>
    <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Hidden links: <%= hidden_links %> · Hidden achievements: <%= hidden_achievements %> · Hidden experience: <%= hidden_experiences %></p>
    <p class="mt-2 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-200">Total secrets: <%= total %></p>
    <p class="mt-2 text-xs text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Remember to drop a subtle hint on your public profile so curious visitors know to open the console.</p>
  </div>
</section>
